        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Correct me if I'm wrong, but I don't think a `on_detach` callback would fix the bug, because `vim.defer_fn` (if invoked from one of the other callbacks before the detach) could defer the request to after the detach.\n\nYou're right. What I mean to say here is that maybe there's a larger issue with the general design of this module, and I would rather address that than adding a local fix.\n\nI'm not completely familiar with this module though, so that's why I would appreciate @ofseed's input here.\n\n",
