            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "It appears this bug is caused by deferring a request in a buffer (loaded), and then, within the very short time before the deferred request is sent, that buffer is unloaded, which triggers the error. Rather than using the loaded-check here, a better approach might be to cancel that deferred request — i.e., stop the timer.\r\n\r\nEdit: I've created a PR for this: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38200.",
